Package Ants

Class Ant

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Thread
Ants.Ant
All Implemented Interfaces:
Dying, Moving, Returning, Runnable
Direct Known Subclasses:
BlueAnt, RedAnt
public abstract class Ant extends Thread implements Returning, Moving, Dying
This abstract class represents an Ant, which runs as a Thread. It includes methods for moving, dying, storing larvae as food, and dropping larvae. It also includes getter and setter methods for various properties of the Ant.
